The '''King of Dale''' was the hereditary ruler of [[Dale (Kingdom)|Dale]], after its foundation by [[Bard]] in {{TA|2944}}, who himself was a descendant of [[Girion]], the last [[Lord of Dale]].<ref name=great>{{App|Great}}</ref>

==List of Kings==
* [[Bard|Bard I]] ({{TA|2944}} - {{TA|2977|n}})<ref name="TA">{{App|TA}}</ref>

* [[Brand]] ({{TA|3007}} - {{TA|3019|n}})<ref name="TA">{{App|TA}}</ref>
* [[Bard II]] (From {{TA|3019}})<ref name="TA">{{App|TA}}</ref>
